snippet: Newcastle United went top of the Championship with a 3-1 win over 10-man Nottingham Forest on Friday while title rivals Brighton and Hove Albion's home match against Cardiff City was postponed because of fog....
lead_paragraph: Newcastle United went top of the Championship with a 3-1 win over 10-man Nottingham Forest on Friday while title rivals Brighton and Hove Albion's home match against Cardiff City was postponed because of fog.

headline.main: Newcastle Go Top With Victory, Brighton Game Called Off
headline.print_headline: Newcastle Go Top With Victory, Brighton Game Called Off
